.SH "EXAMPLES"
.sp
Decode and display the JWT payload (default)
.RS 4
jwt eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.\|.\|.
.RE
.sp
Display the JWT header
.RS 4
jwt \-\-header eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.\|.\|.
.RE
.sp
Display all parts as JSON
.RS 4
jwt \-\-all eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.\|.\|.
.RE
.sp
Verify HMAC signature with secret
.RS 4
jwt \-\-verify=secret123 eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.\|.\|.
.RE
.sp
Verify RSA signature using public key file
.RS 4
jwt \-\-verify=@/path/to/public.pem eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.\|.\|.
.RE
.sp
Verify and show header
.RS 4
jwt \-\-verify=secret123 \-\-header eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.\|.\|.
.RE
.sp
Read token from stdin
.RS 4
echo $TOKEN | jwt
cat token.txt | jwt \-\-header
.RE
.sp
Read key from stdin
.RS 4
echo "secret" | jwt \-v @\- "$TOKEN"
jwt \-v \- "$TOKEN" < keyfile.pem
.RE
